NK102(ne)002:0: phyis 'byung da lta'i tsho ka shi'i lugs dang gcig
NK102(ne)002:1: na dga' ba gcig yin par 'dug bsam nas de
NK102(ne)002:2: gnyis gcig gyur byed kyin 'dug na'ang /
NK102(ne)002:4: ho shang gi lugs dang da lta'i phyag chen 'di gnyis gyu ru lugs su 'dug pa dgongs 'tshal /
NK102(ne)002:7: srid na rnyed daka'i nges gsang dam pa'i chos //
NK102(ne)002:8: yang zab bdud rtsi'i thig phreng 'chi med kyi //
NK102(ne)002:9: go 'phang bcud len sbyin mdzad kun tu bzang //
NK102(ne)002:10: dang po'i mgon de'i rtogs pa'i 'dra 'bag dngos /
NK102(ne)002:12: 1 / rgyal rnams bsam gtan mchog 'dir brten byas nas //
NK102(ne)002:13: byang chub mchog gi mig bzang rnyed pa las //
NK102(ne)002:14: srid gsum mun stug gsal ba'i sgron me che //
NK102(ne)002:15: shes rab ye shes 'od chen de kho na /
NK102(ne)002:17: 2 / brgyud gsum rig 'dzin bla ma'i zhal gyi lung //
NK102(ne)002:18: sangs rgyas ye shes gang thugs za ma tog /
NK102(ne)002:19: nor bu'i sgrom bu bskyil ba phyi rab kyi //
NK102(ne)002:20: skal bzang dbang rab don du legs par phyungs /
NK102(ne)002:22: 3 / rim dang cig char 'jug pa'i ting 'dzin sgo //
NK102(ne)002:23: 'bum phrag mdo sngags rin chen lde mig gis //
NK102(ne)002:24: legs par 'byed pa'i rdo rje'i glegs bu 'di //
NK102(ne)002:25: mthong dang thos rnams srid pa tha mar nges /
NK102(ne)002:27: 4 / sngon byon rig 'dzin rnams la rlung ltar grags //
NK102(ne)002:28: phyis dus nam mkha'i ngogs su rgyas btab snyam //
NK102(ne)002:29: deng dus kun mkhyen bla ma kahthoga pas //
NK102(ne)002:30: bde ldan zhing nas gter chen 'di rnyed rgyal /
NK102(ne)002:32: 5 / rdo rje 'chang dbang pad+ma bi dza ya'i //
NK102(ne)002:33: thugs dgongs rdzogs phyir dge legs rgya mtsho ches //
NK102(ne)002:34: gtong ba'i nor gyi sprin chen bres pa dang //
NK102(ne)002:35: zhing skyong lhag bsam dbyar bya mkha' la 'phyo /
NK102(ne)002:37: 6 / chos sbyin 'dzad med par gyi 'phrul chen 'dir //
NK102(ne)002:38: brtson pa'i legs byas gangs ri'i rjes 'gro ba //
NK102(ne)002:39: sras bcas rgyal ba'i yongs bsngosa thabs chen gyis //
NK102(ne)002:40: bla ma'i zab dbyings rab tu mnyes phyir bsngo /
NK102(ne)002:42: 7 / mkha' mnyam yid can bgrangs las 'das pa rnams //
NK102(ne)002:43: de bzhin gshegs dag'i bsam gtan bde thob nas //
NK102(ne)002:44: rnam grol zhi ba chos sku'i rgyal khams der //
NK102(ne)002:45: bde blag nyid du phyin pa'i mthu thob shog 8 /
NK102(ne)002:46: chos tshul 'di yang nub med dar zhing rgyas //
NK102(ne)002:47: ting 'dzin rtsal chen nyi zla'i bgrod pa las //
NK102(ne)002:48: myur ba'i lam mchog bden don mngon gyur te //
NK102(ne)002:49: mchog dngos grub pas nor 'dzin khyab gyur cig 9 /
NK102(ne)002:50: snod bcud rgud pa'i gdung ba zhi ba dang //
NK102(ne)002:51: chos 'di'i byin rlabs drod kyi legs bsrings pas //
NK102(ne)002:52: bskal bzang rdzogs ldan snye ma gsar pa la //
NK102(ne)002:53: ci dgar spyod pa'i bkra shis nub med shog 10 /
NK102(ne)002:54: ces pa'ang skyabs rje ze chen pa pad+ma'i mtshan can gyi gsung gi bdud rtsis 'tsho zhing /
NK102(ne)002:55: rgyal ba kahthoga pa chen po'i bka' 'bangs kyi tha
NK102(ne)002:56: chung 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i phrin las kyi byed por
NK102(ne)002:57: yi dam bca' ba 'jam dbyangs blo gros rgya mtshos
